Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:29.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:865323,869786}When I'm waiting like this, I feel like I'm going to hear Tsutomu-kun's footsteps any second.{NOTE:こうして待ってるといつも努くんの足音が近づいてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:30.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:869786,870953}But it won't happen…{NOTE:でももう…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:37.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:875458,877168}Tsutomu-kun!?{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.54,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:881130,883549}I'm guessing you didn't get much sleep.{NOTE:ずっと眠ってないですってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:45.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:883549,885343}Are you going to quit volleyball?{NOTE:バレーも止めるですってね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:885343,888096}I wouldn't blame you. I'd understand.{NOTE:無理もないわ。私も賛成よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:888096,889222}Midori…{NOTE:みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:889222,891641}I'd probably do the same if I were in your shoes.{NOTE:私だって当然そうするでしょうね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:55.22,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:893684,895228}So what are you going to do now?{NOTE:これからどうす？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:895228,897146}I don't know…{NOTE:これから？分からない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:897146,898981}I don't know anything.{NOTE:何もかも分からないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:898981,900733}There's nothing left for me anymore.{NOTE:私には何も残ってないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:900733,902193}Get a grip already!{NOTE:いい加減にしてよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:902193,903986}What the heck, Midori?{NOTE:何ですって？みどり。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.78,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:903986,906781}Not accepting reality isn't like you at all, Kozue!{NOTE:現実から目を逸らすなんてこずえらしくないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.28,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:906781,908282}I can understand the shock.{NOTE:ショックは分かるけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.41,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:908282,910410}But wallowing in despair all by yourself…{NOTE:自分勝手な絶望に溺れるなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:13.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:910410,913454}Didn't Tsutomu-kun despise that kind of behavior?{NOTE:努さんが聞いたら、それこそお笑いだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:913454,914580}Despise?{NOTE:お笑い？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:15.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:914580,915957}I guess you're right. Heh.{NOTE:聞こえたらね。ふふ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.95,0:15:16.91,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:915957,916916}Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.62,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:916916,919627}Stop hurting yourself!{NOTE:そんな言い方で自分を傷つけるような真似はやめて！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:919627,921462}Tsutomu-kun would hate this.{NOTE:努さんの大嫌いなことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:921462,922713}Spare me that.{NOTE:止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:922713,925508}You don't understand my feelings.{NOTE:あなたには私の気持ちなんか分かってないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.67,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:925508,927677}No, I don't.{NOTE:ええ。分からないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:32.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:927677,932181}However, Tsutomu-san never let any situation stop him, no matter how difficult it was.{NOTE:ただ努さんはどんな苦しい境遇に置かれてもくじけなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.55,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:932181,934559}In fact, the more difficult it was…{NOTE:いいえ。それが苦しければ苦しいほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.76,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:934559,936769}…the more motivated he was\Nto face it and crush it.{NOTE:よりファイト燃やして立ち向かっていった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:936769,938396}Unlike how you're being!{NOTE:あなたと違って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:938396,940815}That's easy for you to say, Midori…{NOTE:みどり！あなたは何でも言える！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:44.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:940815,944444}…since you and Mitamura-kun are both alive!{NOTE:だってあなたと三田村くんは今生きてるんですもの！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:46.32,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:944444,946320}Kozue!{NOTE:—こずえ！\\N—あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:946320,948573}I'm sorry for that.{NOTE:叩いてのは悪かったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:49.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:948573,949574}But…{NOTE:でも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.49,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:949574,951492}That was…{NOTE:いくら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.66,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:951492,953661}You shouldn't have said that.{NOTE:XXXしてるからって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.49,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:953661,956497}I might be your best friend, but even I have my limits.{NOTE:そんな言い方例え親友でも我慢できないわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:957707,958708}Fine.{NOTE:結構よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:958708,961043}Keep serving me all the lectures you want.{NOTE:だったら結構でもなんでもしてちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:05.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:961043,965590}But there's no way you'll ever\Nunderstand what I'm going through.{NOTE:どうせ私の気持ちなんて他人のあなたに分かるわけがないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:965590,967091}Stop acting like a spoiled child!{NOTE:甘ったれないでよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:967091,968426}Oh, so now you'll slap me from the left?{NOTE:今度は左の方？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:968426,969594}I've had enough!{NOTE:もうたくさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:10.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:969594,970344}Hold on!{NOTE:待って！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:972054,973681}One more thing.{NOTE:もう一つだけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:19.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:973681,979312}If you give up on volleyball like this, you'll be hurting Tsutomu-kun the most.{NOTE:これっきりあなたがバレーを捨てるようなことになれば一番悲しむは努さんだってこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:979312,981230}Keep that in mind.{NOTE:それ覚えといて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.63,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007840,1009634}You have to catch up to the ball faster!{NOTE:早く飛び込んで広うのよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.51,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010510,1011511}Ah, shoot.{NOTE:しまった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.51,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011511,1013513}Alright! Ten minute break!{NOTE:よし！十分間休憩！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.26,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017058,1018267}Professor Hongou.{NOTE:本郷先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:00.93,Default,Oonuma,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018267,1020937}Is Ayuhara-san really going to quit volleyball?{NOTE:本当に鮎原さんはバレーを止めるでしょうか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:01.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020937,1021562}Hmm.{NOTE:んん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.23,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022688,1025233}I talked with her mother over the phone just a while ago.{NOTE:さっきも母様と電話で話したんですけどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.19,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025233,1027193}It looks like she shut herself in her room.{NOTE:お部屋に閉じこもったXXそうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.19,0:17:11.73,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027193,1031739}But I can't believe that Chief could just let go of volleyball.{NOTE:でも信じられないわ。親分がバレーを本当に止めるなんてさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:13.15,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031739,1033157}Ayuhara is serious.{NOTE:鮎原は本気だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.99,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033157,1035993}It's just that she can't think about volleyball at the moment.{NOTE:いや、バレーの事など眼中にはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:20.08,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035993,1040081}Either way, this is going to have great influence over Ayuhara's future.{NOTE:いずれにしても。それで鮎原の今後の生き方が決まる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.00,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043334,1047004}Kozue will definitely come back to this court.{NOTE:こずえは必ず戻ってくる。このコートに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.67,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047004,1049674}I can't imagine any other future for Kozue.{NOTE:それ以外にこずえの生きる道がない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:47.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064230,1067483}There's nothing left for me anymore.{NOTE:もう私には何も残っていない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067483,1069443}Only memories of Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努くんとの思えでだけ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.69,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069443,1071696}Other than that, there's nothing at all…{NOTE:後にも先にも何もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.03,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071696,1073030}Kozue-chan.{NOTE:こずえちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:53.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073030,1073948}Oh, it's you, Auntie.{NOTE:おばさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.45,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076158,1077451}Kozue-chan.{NOTE:こずえちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.95,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077451,1079954}I'm not going to tell you to try and forget about Tsutomu.{NOTE:努のことを忘れてくれとは言わないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.79,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079954,1083791}But you're going to get sick\Nif you don't go outside.{NOTE:いつまでもふさぎこんでいては肝心なあなたが病気になってしまうわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.37,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083791,1085376}Cheer up a little.{NOTE:元気を出してちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:05.96,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085376,1085960}Okay?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:06.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085960,1086502}Yeah…{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:09.63,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086502,1089630}Actually, I have some of his belongings with me.{NOTE:実はね。形見分けと言うつもりなんだけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.38,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089630,1092383}I thought that it'd be better to give it to you.{NOTE:これはあなたにあげたほうがいいと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092383,1094802}Tsutomu-kun's diary?{NOTE:努くんの日記？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.30,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1094802,1096304}Diary{NOTE:日記帳}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.51,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097179,1099515}Thank you, Auntie.{NOTE:有難う、おばさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:22.43,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099515,1102435}It may awaken some hurting memories…{NOTE:又辛い思い出を呼び覚ますかもしれないけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:26.68,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102435,1106689}…but I think you'll also find some happiness in there, even if it's just a little bit.{NOTE:本当は思い出は思い出として、あなたにもう一度元気になってほしいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:28.81,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108024,1108816}Thank you.{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.69,Default,Ichinose's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112486,1114697}I'm sure Tsutomu would've liked it this way.{NOTE:努もきっと喜ぶわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.16,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117116,1119160}Tsutomu-kun's diary…{NOTE:努くんの日記。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:43.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119160,1123914}I'm pressing to my chest everything he didn't show to anyone until now.{NOTE:誰にも見せない努くんのすべてを今私がこの胸に抱きしめている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:53.04,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1127084,1133049}Diary{NOTE:日記帳}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128169,1131505}This book holds all the memories of Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努くんの思い出がこの中に全部あるんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:55.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131505,1135468}With this, I can meet with Tsutomu-kun one more time.{NOTE:私はもう一度努くんとこの中で会えるんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139639,1142475}"New Year's Day, 1970."{NOTE:「昭和45年元旦。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:06.39,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142475,1146395}"I'm going to confess to myself."{NOTE:「僕は念頭にあたって自分自身に告白する。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146395,1149231}"I'm in love with Ayuhara Kozue."{NOTE:「僕は鮎原こずえを愛している。」}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149231,1150733}"In love"!?{NOTE:愛している？！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.90,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151567,1153903}But I'm not going to tell it to her…{NOTE:しかし、この心打ち明け来るときは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.73,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153903,1156739}…until she becomes the best attacker in the world.{NOTE:…鮎原こずえが世界のアタックナンバーワンに成る時だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:20.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158324,1160117}The best attacker in the world!{NOTE:世界のアタックナンバーワン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.78,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1160117,1163788}World's Attack no. 1{NOTE:世界のアタックナンバーワン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:27.24,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164455,1167249}The best attacker in the world!{NOTE:世界の…アタックナンバーワン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168209,1169251}Tsutomu-kun…!{NOTE:努くんが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:35.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172797,1175341}These pictures and data are all about me!{NOTE:私の写真とデータ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175341,1176592}He went this far?!{NOTE:こんなにまで！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:45.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182723,1185351}Through all of this just for me…?{NOTE:こ、こんなにも私のために努くんが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:52.69,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190231,1192692}At first, I was jealous.{NOTE:初めのころ僕は悩んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:56.86,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192692,1196862}Kozue-kun puts so much effort into volleyball\Nthat there is no room for me to enter.{NOTE:こずえくんがあまりにもバレーに打ち込み、僕など入り込む余地もなくんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:20:00.15,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196862,1200157}Around that time I hated volleyball from the bottom of my heart.{NOTE:そのころは僕は心からバレーを憎んだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.66,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200157,1203661}But I quickly realized that it was selfish and immature.{NOTE:でも、それは目先だけのわがままだと分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:07.33,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203661,1207331}I have my dreams too, just like Kozue-kun has her volleyball.{NOTE:僕には僕の進むべき精神があり、こずえ君のそれはバレーだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.62,0:20:11.41,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209625,1211419}I understood that…{NOTE:その時僕に分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:15.92,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211419,1215923}…we have to devote ourselves to our talents for the sake of our futures.{NOTE:僕たちの未来のために僕たちはお互いの青春を豊かなものにしなければと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:19.96,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215923,1219969}What made me realize it was\Nhow important volleyball is to Kozue-kun.{NOTE:それを教えてくれたのはこずえくんがひたすらバレーに打ち込む姿である。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:22.93,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219969,1222930}But also the pleasure I take in my work.{NOTE:もう一つは僕自身働く喜びだった。}
